<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="List_of_best-selling_individual_books">List of best-selling individual books</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_best-selling_books&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: List of best-selling individual books">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
