<li id="cite_note-34"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/books-life/7545438/The-20-greatest-childrens-books-ever.html">The Telegraph</a> on <i>The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe</i>: "This classic story has sold more than 85 million copies in 29 different languages since its publication in 1950." (3 April 2010)</span></li>
